ps://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>在回合制战术游戏<a href="https://www.nme.com/games/the-lamplighters-league"><em>The Lamplighters League</em></a>推出仅两周后， <a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/paradox-interactive">Paradox Interactive</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/brands/harebrained-schemes">Harebrained Plannings</a>就宣布分道扬镳。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/gaming-news/exclusive-check-out-jon-everists-jazzy-main-theme-for-the-lamplighters-league-3506402">独家：看看 Jon Everist 为“The Lamplighters League”创作的爵士主题曲</a></strong></li></ul><p>10 月 10 日，Paradox Interactive 表示，由于商业反响不温不火，该游戏<a href="https://www.paradoxinteractive.com/media/press-releases/press-release/paradox-interactive-writes-down-msek-171-of-capitalized-development-cost-for-the-lamplighters-league">“非常令人失望”</a> 。 <em>《点灯者联盟》的</em>背景设定在 1930 年代的另一个版本中，玩家必须阻止邪教夺取珍贵的文物来统治世界。</p><p>该游戏于 10 月 3 日推出，适用于<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/pc">PC</a> 、 <a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-one">Xbox One</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-series-xs">Xbox Series X|S</a> ，并可通过<a href="https://www.nme.com/tag/xbox-game-pass">Xbox Game Pass</a>进行游戏。 </p><figure id="attachment_3517143" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3517143" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3517143" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-3.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-3.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-3-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-3-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-3-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-3-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-3-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3517143" class="wp-caption-text"> 《点灯者联盟》图片来源：Paradox Interactive</figcaption></figure><p> “游戏项目本质上总是有风险的，但最终我们并没有达到我们应有的水平。这很痛苦，但让我们更加渴望卷起袖子做得更好，”Paradox Interactive 首席执行官 Fredrik Wester 在最初的公告中说道。</p><p>现在，Paradox Interactive 和 Harebrained Schemes 表示，从 2024 年 1 月 1 日起，两家公司将不再合作。</p><p>该出版商在昨天（10 月 17 日）的<a href="https://www.paradoxinteractive.com/media/press-releases/press-release/harebrained-schemes-and-paradox-interactive-to-part-ways-as-the-seattle-based-developer-seeks-new-opportunities" target="_blank" rel="noopener">一份声明</a>中表示：“此次分离是双方达成一致的结果，源于双方的战略和创意优先事项。”</p><p>首席运营官 Charlotta Nilsson 还补充说，Paradox Interactive 已“重新将战略重点转向具有无尽品质的策略和管理游戏的核心领域”。 </p><figure id="attachment_3517145" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3517145" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="size-full wp-image-3517145" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-2.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-and-harebrained-schemes-announce-split-2.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/paradox-